<subSubSection id="C359656166208077FF6AFB2AFED0FB3F" pageId="1" pageNumber="143" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="8BFC36EA66208077FF6AFB2AFED0FB3F" blockId="1.[151,1437,403,1978]" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">
<emphasis id="B937EAF866208077FF6AFB2AFEEBFB13" bold="true" box="[199,334,1195,1221]" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">Etymology.</emphasis>
The new species name is derived from Latin words “ 
<emphasis id="B937EAF866208077FC19FB2DFC46FB13" box="[948,995,1196,1221]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">nigr</emphasis>
” and “ 
<emphasis id="B937EAF866208077FB98FB2AFBC2FB13" box="[1077,1127,1195,1221]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">limb</emphasis>
” referring to the pronotum with black margins.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C359656166208077FF6AFB72FC6AF86F" pageId="1" pageNumber="143" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BFC36EA66208077FF6AFB72FC6AF86F" blockId="1.[151,1437,403,1978]" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">
<emphasis id="B937EAF866208077FF6AFB72FEE9FADB" bold="true" box="[199,332,1267,1293]" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">Discussion.</emphasis>
According to the female seventh abdominal sternite with transverse fold and subgenital plate with 1 pair of tubercles, we place the new species under the 
<taxonomicName id="4C434D6966208077FCB9FA96FAB2FAE7" baseAuthorityName="Griffini" baseAuthorityYear="1914" box="[788,1303,1303,1330]" class="Insecta" family="Gryllacrididae" genus="Metriogryllacris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="143" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="amitarum" subGenus="Metriogryllacris">
<emphasis id="B937EAF866208077FCB9FA96FC68FAE7" box="[788,973,1303,1329]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">Metriogryllacris</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="B937EAF866208077FC72FA96FB3DFAE7" box="[991,1176,1303,1329]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">Metriogryllacris</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis id="B937EAF866208077FB07FA99FAB2FAE7" box="[1194,1303,1304,1329]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">amitarum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group. The new species differs from 
<taxonomicName id="4C434D6966208077FE18FABAFBC8FA83" authority="(Griffini, 1914)" baseAuthorityName="Griffini" baseAuthorityYear="1914" box="[437,1133,1339,1366]" class="Insecta" family="Gryllacrididae" genus="Metriogryllacris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="143" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="amitarum" subGenus="Metriogryllacris">
<emphasis id="B937EAF866208077FE18FABAFDCBFA83" box="[437,622,1339,1365]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">Metriogryllacris</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="B937EAF866208077FDD2FABAFC9DFA83" box="[639,824,1339,1365]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">Metriogryllacris</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis id="B937EAF866208077FCE7FABDFC12FA83" box="[842,951,1340,1365]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">amitarum</emphasis>
(Griffini, 1914)
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C434D6966208077FB08FABAFDFCFAAF" authority="Gorochov, 2004" authorityName="Gorochov" authorityYear="2004" class="Insecta" family="Gryllacrididae" genus="Metriogryllacris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="143" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="distincta" subGenus="Metriogryllacris">
<emphasis id="B937EAF866208077FB08FABAFAFBFA83" box="[1189,1374,1339,1365]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">Metriogryllacris</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="B937EAF866208077FAC2FABDFE89FAAF" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">Metriogryllacris</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis id="B937EAF866208077FE90FADEFE38FAAF" box="[317,413,1375,1401]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">distincta</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFD24B1B66208077FE08FADEFDFCFAAF" author="Gorochov, A. V." box="[421,601,1375,1401]" pageId="1" pageNumber="143" pagination="900 - 921" refId="ref2795" refString="Gorochov, A. V. (2004) Contribution to the Knowledge of the Fauna and Systematics of the Stenopelmatoidea (Orthoptera) of Indochina and Some Other Territories. V. Entomologicheskoe Obozrenie, 83 (4), 816 - 841. [in Russian; English translation: A Contribution to the Fauna and Systematics of Stenopelmatoidea (Orthoptera) of Indochina and Some Other Territories: V. Entomological Review, 84 (8), 900 - 921]" type="journal article" year="2004">Gorochov, 2004</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
by: pronotum with black margins which widened at anterior and posterior margins; the transverse fold of female seventh abdominal sternite crescent-shaped; female subgenital plate with 1 pair of small tubercles, posterior margin widely rounded; ovipositor about 0.67 times as long as hind femur, basal processes of ventrovalvulae lobate with widely arched apices. While 
<taxonomicName id="4C434D6966208077FC30FA4AFEEDF9DF" authority="(Griffini, 1914)" baseAuthorityName="Griffini" baseAuthorityYear="1914" class="Insecta" family="Gryllacrididae" genus="Metriogryllacris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="143" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="amitarum" subGenus="Metriogryllacris">
<emphasis id="B937EAF866208077FC30FA4AFBF3FA33" box="[925,1110,1483,1509]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">Metriogryllacris</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="B937EAF866208077FBCBFA4AFABAFA33" box="[1126,1311,1483,1509]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">Metriogryllacris</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis id="B937EAF866208077FA82FA4DFA39FA33" box="[1327,1436,1484,1509]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">amitarum</emphasis>
(Griffini, 1914)
</taxonomicName>
has pronotum with black margins, black median band on disc and yellowish longitudinal spots on lateral lobes (
<bibRefCitation id="EFD24B1B66208077FEF8F992FDB4F9FB" author="Gorochov, A. V." box="[341,529,1555,1581]" pageId="1" pageNumber="143" pagination="900 - 921" refId="ref2795" refString="Gorochov, A. V. (2004) Contribution to the Knowledge of the Fauna and Systematics of the Stenopelmatoidea (Orthoptera) of Indochina and Some Other Territories. V. Entomologicheskoe Obozrenie, 83 (4), 816 - 841. [in Russian; English translation: A Contribution to the Fauna and Systematics of Stenopelmatoidea (Orthoptera) of Indochina and Some Other Territories: V. Entomological Review, 84 (8), 900 - 921]" type="journal article" year="2004">Gorochov, 2004</bibRefCitation>
: Fig. 18; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFD24B1B66208077FDD3F992FC80F9FB" author="Ingrisch, S." box="[638,805,1555,1581]" pageId="1" pageNumber="143" pagination="1 - 278" refId="ref2880" refString="Ingrisch, S. (2018) New taxa and records of Gryllacrididae (Orthoptera, Stenopelmatoidea) from South East Asia and New Guinea with a key to the genera. Zootaxa, 4510 (1), 1 - 278 https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4510.1.1" type="journal article" year="2018">Ingrisch, 2018</bibRefCitation>
: Fig. 76C–E); the transverse fold of seventh abdominal sternite semi-circular; ventral surface of subgenital plate with 1 pair of conical processes (
<bibRefCitation id="EFD24B1B66208077FB0BF9B6FAC6F987" author="Gorochov, A. V." box="[1190,1379,1591,1617]" pageId="1" pageNumber="143" pagination="900 - 921" refId="ref2795" refString="Gorochov, A. V. (2004) Contribution to the Knowledge of the Fauna and Systematics of the Stenopelmatoidea (Orthoptera) of Indochina and Some Other Territories. V. Entomologicheskoe Obozrenie, 83 (4), 816 - 841. [in Russian; English translation: A Contribution to the Fauna and Systematics of Stenopelmatoidea (Orthoptera) of Indochina and Some Other Territories: V. Entomological Review, 84 (8), 900 - 921]" type="journal article" year="2004">Gorochov, 2004</bibRefCitation>
: Fig. 29), apical area projected, posterior margin narrowly rounded; ovipositor 0.6 times as long as hind femur, basal processes of ventrovalvulae with obtuse apices (
<bibRefCitation id="EFD24B1B66208077FD1DF9FEFCCFF94F" author="Gorochov, A. V." box="[688,874,1663,1689]" pageId="1" pageNumber="143" pagination="900 - 921" refId="ref2795" refString="Gorochov, A. V. (2004) Contribution to the Knowledge of the Fauna and Systematics of the Stenopelmatoidea (Orthoptera) of Indochina and Some Other Territories. V. Entomologicheskoe Obozrenie, 83 (4), 816 - 841. [in Russian; English translation: A Contribution to the Fauna and Systematics of Stenopelmatoidea (Orthoptera) of Indochina and Some Other Territories: V. Entomological Review, 84 (8), 900 - 921]" type="journal article" year="2004">Gorochov, 2004</bibRefCitation>
: Fig. 29; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFD24B1B66208077FC7CF9FEFB3AF94C" author="Ingrisch, S." box="[977,1183,1663,1690]" pageId="1" pageNumber="143" pagination="1 - 278" refId="ref2880" refString="Ingrisch, S. (2018) New taxa and records of Gryllacrididae (Orthoptera, Stenopelmatoidea) from South East Asia and New Guinea with a key to the genera. Zootaxa, 4510 (1), 1 - 278 https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4510.1.1" type="journal article" year="2018">Ingrisch, 2018: 77</bibRefCitation>
L). In 
<taxonomicName id="4C434D6966208077FB4EF9FEFD21F96B" authority="Gorochov, 2004" authorityName="Gorochov" authorityYear="2004" class="Insecta" family="Gryllacrididae" genus="Metriogryllacris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="143" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="distincta" subGenus="Metriogryllacris">
<emphasis id="B937EAF866208077FB4EF9FEFA39F94F" box="[1251,1436,1663,1689]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">Metriogryllacris</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="B937EAF866208077FF0CF922FEFFF96B" box="[161,346,1699,1725]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">Metriogryllacris</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis id="B937EAF866208077FEC5F922FE6DF96B" box="[360,456,1699,1725]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">distincta</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFD24B1B66208077FE63F922FD21F96B" author="Gorochov, A. V." box="[462,644,1699,1725]" pageId="1" pageNumber="143" pagination="900 - 921" refId="ref2795" refString="Gorochov, A. V. (2004) Contribution to the Knowledge of the Fauna and Systematics of the Stenopelmatoidea (Orthoptera) of Indochina and Some Other Territories. V. Entomologicheskoe Obozrenie, 83 (4), 816 - 841. [in Russian; English translation: A Contribution to the Fauna and Systematics of Stenopelmatoidea (Orthoptera) of Indochina and Some Other Territories: V. Entomological Review, 84 (8), 900 - 921]" type="journal article" year="2004">Gorochov, 2004</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, pronotum with black margins, narrow brown or black spots on disc and larger yellowish spots on lateral lobes (
<bibRefCitation id="EFD24B1B66208077FDFDF946FCAEF937" author="Gorochov, A. V." box="[592,779,1735,1761]" pageId="1" pageNumber="143" pagination="900 - 921" refId="ref2795" refString="Gorochov, A. V. (2004) Contribution to the Knowledge of the Fauna and Systematics of the Stenopelmatoidea (Orthoptera) of Indochina and Some Other Territories. V. Entomologicheskoe Obozrenie, 83 (4), 816 - 841. [in Russian; English translation: A Contribution to the Fauna and Systematics of Stenopelmatoidea (Orthoptera) of Indochina and Some Other Territories: V. Entomological Review, 84 (8), 900 - 921]" type="journal article" year="2004">Gorochov, 2004</bibRefCitation>
: Fig. 14); the transverse fold of female seventh abdominal sternite crescent-shaped; ventral surface of female subgenital plate with 1 pair of long conical processes, posterior margin widely rounded (
<bibRefCitation id="EFD24B1B66208077FE00F88EFDCDF8FF" author="Gorochov, A. V." box="[429,616,1807,1833]" pageId="1" pageNumber="143" pagination="900 - 921" refId="ref2795" refString="Gorochov, A. V. (2004) Contribution to the Knowledge of the Fauna and Systematics of the Stenopelmatoidea (Orthoptera) of Indochina and Some Other Territories. V. Entomologicheskoe Obozrenie, 83 (4), 816 - 841. [in Russian; English translation: A Contribution to the Fauna and Systematics of Stenopelmatoidea (Orthoptera) of Indochina and Some Other Territories: V. Entomological Review, 84 (8), 900 - 921]" type="journal article" year="2004">Gorochov, 2004</bibRefCitation>
: Fig. 28); ovipositor about half as long as hind femur, basal processes of ventrovalvulae spine-shaped with subacute apices (
<bibRefCitation id="EFD24B1B66208077FD7CF8B2FC2FF89B" author="Gorochov, A. V." box="[721,906,1843,1869]" pageId="1" pageNumber="143" pagination="900 - 921" refId="ref2795" refString="Gorochov, A. V. (2004) Contribution to the Knowledge of the Fauna and Systematics of the Stenopelmatoidea (Orthoptera) of Indochina and Some Other Territories. V. Entomologicheskoe Obozrenie, 83 (4), 816 - 841. [in Russian; English translation: A Contribution to the Fauna and Systematics of Stenopelmatoidea (Orthoptera) of Indochina and Some Other Territories: V. Entomological Review, 84 (8), 900 - 921]" type="journal article" year="2004">Gorochov, 2004</bibRefCitation>
: Fig. 28). Based on the description of the above two known species by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFD24B1B66208077FE34F8D6FDFEF8A7" author="Gorochov, A. V." box="[409,603,1879,1905]" pageId="1" pageNumber="143" pagination="900 - 921" refId="ref2795" refString="Gorochov, A. V. (2004) Contribution to the Knowledge of the Fauna and Systematics of the Stenopelmatoidea (Orthoptera) of Indochina and Some Other Territories. V. Entomologicheskoe Obozrenie, 83 (4), 816 - 841. [in Russian; English translation: A Contribution to the Fauna and Systematics of Stenopelmatoidea (Orthoptera) of Indochina and Some Other Territories: V. Entomological Review, 84 (8), 900 - 921]" type="journal article" year="2004">Gorochov (2004)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation id="EFD24B1B66208077FD3EF8D6FCE4F8A7" author="Ingrisch, S." box="[659,833,1879,1905]" pageId="1" pageNumber="143" pagination="1 - 278" refId="ref2880" refString="Ingrisch, S. (2018) New taxa and records of Gryllacrididae (Orthoptera, Stenopelmatoidea) from South East Asia and New Guinea with a key to the genera. Zootaxa, 4510 (1), 1 - 278 https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4510.1.1" type="journal article" year="2018">Ingrisch (2018)</bibRefCitation>
and the specimens from 
<collectingRegion id="4987F80866208077FBF1F8D6FB02F8A7" box="[1116,1191,1879,1905]" country="China" name="Fujian" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">Fujian</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion id="4987F80866208077FB1EF8D6FAB6F8A7" box="[1203,1299,1879,1905]" country="China" name="Guangxi" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">Guangxi</collectingRegion>
and 
<collectingRegion id="4987F80866208077FAE6F8D9FA3DF8A4" box="[1355,1432,1880,1906]" country="China" name="Hunan" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">Hunan</collectingRegion>
, we think the Chinese specimens originally treated as 
<taxonomicName id="4C434D6966208077FD44F8FAFA39F843" authority="(Griffini, 1914)" baseAuthorityName="Griffini" baseAuthorityYear="1914" box="[745,1436,1915,1942]" class="Insecta" family="Gryllacrididae" genus="Metriogryllacris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="143" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="amitarum" subGenus="Metriogryllacris">
<emphasis id="B937EAF866208077FD44F8FAFC07F843" box="[745,930,1915,1941]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">Metriogryllacris</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="B937EAF866208077FC1FF8FAFBCEF843" box="[946,1131,1915,1941]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">Metriogryllacris</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis id="B937EAF866208077FBD6F8FDFB4DF843" box="[1147,1256,1916,1941]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">amitarum</emphasis>
(Griffini, 1914)
</taxonomicName>
may be the 
<taxonomicName id="4C434D6966208077FEB4F81EFC6EF86F" authority="Gorochov, 2004" authorityName="Gorochov" authorityYear="2004" box="[281,971,1951,1978]" class="Insecta" family="Gryllacrididae" genus="Metriogryllacris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="143" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="distincta" subGenus="Metriogryllacris">
<emphasis id="B937EAF866208077FEB4F81EFE77F86F" box="[281,466,1951,1977]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">Metriogryllacris</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="B937EAF866208077FE4FF81EFD3EF86F" box="[482,667,1951,1977]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">Metriogryllacris</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis id="B937EAF866208077FD01F81EFCA9F86F" box="[684,780,1951,1977]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">distincta</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFD24B1B66208077FCBEF81EFC6EF86F" author="Gorochov, A. V." box="[787,971,1951,1977]" pageId="1" pageNumber="143" pagination="900 - 921" refId="ref2795" refString="Gorochov, A. V. (2004) Contribution to the Knowledge of the Fauna and Systematics of the Stenopelmatoidea (Orthoptera) of Indochina and Some Other Territories. V. Entomologicheskoe Obozrenie, 83 (4), 816 - 841. [in Russian; English translation: A Contribution to the Fauna and Systematics of Stenopelmatoidea (Orthoptera) of Indochina and Some Other Territories: V. Entomological Review, 84 (8), 900 - 921]" type="journal article" year="2004">Gorochov, 2004</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
